                                    <ns0:p>Two fragments of a large, thick plaque(?) of limestone; joined together with plaster when seen by Bivona, but seemingly not actually joining, with a gap of at least 2-3 letters in between (as proposed by Mommsen). Fragment A (left) is H 29 x W 47 x D 18 cm; Fragment B (right) is H 31 x W 68 x D 20 (measurements by Bivona).</ns0:p>
